# Substack Post – Day 07

## Title:
The Future of Evolving NFTs — How BubuVerse Sets a New Standard

## Summary:
This Substack issue explores why evolving NFTs are the next major step for Web3. It explains how Bubus can transform, gain abilities, and become living digital entities—turning NFTs into dynamic companions rather than static assets.

